issue.title: Default values for date and time in event create and edit
issue.body: The default date and time are hardcoded into the HTML. In addition, it doesn't make sense to even have a default for editing, since its standard behaviour should be to not change date (i.e. blank)

issue.title: Error going to nonexistent URL for /view/event/
issue.body: Python dies with an UnboundLocalError if you attempt at access a nonexistent event

issue.title: Error searching blank string
issue.body: Python dies if you search an empty string with a TypeError on NoneType

issue.title: Password field too short
issue.body: MD5 is 32 characters; field only allows 30.

issue.title: Duration maximised at 9 hours
issue.body: Totally arbitrary, done for database integrity reasons. Logically, should be 24.

issue.title: Upcoming event table
issue.body: Upcoming event tables on the buskers profile are poorly formatted and the table often are either not centralised or go off the page on mobiles.

issue.title: Event preview bubbles on map
issue.body: We should only allow one open at a time, it becomes very messy otherwise
